TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Determination of Marginal Cost Prices under a Set of Axioms
AU  - Samet, Dov
AU  - Tauman, Yair
AB  - [This paper presents a set of axioms which characterize a family of price mechanisms for consumption goods, including marginal cost prices and Aumann-Shapley prices. By strengthening one of the axioms, marginal cost prices are characterized and by requiring that cost is shared the Aumann-Shapley prices are characterized. A discussion of the economic interpretation of the axioms is also provided.]
