TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Nonparametric Approach to Demand Analysis
AU  - Varian, Hal R.
AB  - [This paper shows how to test data for consistency with utility maximization, recover the underlying preferences, and forecast demand behavior without making any assumptions concerning the parametric form of the underlying utility or demand functions.]
